540
00:54:27,800 --> 00:54:31,997
格伦.瑞科尔及安.比斯霍普为您报导
Ann Bishop, and the award-winning Newswatch team.

541
00:54:32,337 --> 00:54:34,771
晚上好 我是悠视网络电视的格伦.瑞科
Good evening. I'm Glen Rinker, Newswatch Ten.

542
00:54:34,973 --> 00:54:38,101
