548
00:54:53,790 --> 00:54:55,690
高速公路已为雪堆所堵塞
Highways are blocked by snowdrifts.

549
00:54:55,892 --> 00:54:57,655
铁轨已经结冰
Railroad tracks are frozen.

550
00:54:57,860 --> 00:54:59,885
科罗拉多州官方向悠视网络电视透露
Officials in Colorado tell Newswatch...

551
00:55:00,096 --> 00:55:03,656
至少有三人已由于暴露于暴风雪中致死
at least 3 have been killed by exposure to freezing winds.

552
00:55:03,865 --> 00:55:06,163
科罗拉多州长可能
The governor of Colorado is expected...

553
00:55:06,368 --> 00:55:08,097
