你对这儿根本就没兴趣
That you haven't the belly for it.

911
01:32:57,595 --> 01:33:01,895
再给我次机会证明自己吧 格兰蒂先生
Just give me one more chance to prove it, Mr. Grady.

912
01:33:02,733 --> 01:33:04,667
我就这么点要求
That's all I ask.

913
01:33:06,203 --> 01:33:10,469
你妻子看来比我们想象的要坚强得多 托兰斯先生
Your wife appears to be stronger than we imagined, Mr. Torrance.

914
01:33:10,674 --> 01:33:12,141
而且比想象的更
Somewhat more...

915
01:33:12,342 --> 01:33:14,309
足智多谋
...resourceful.

916
01:33:14,577 --> 01:33:17,341
她好象比你要强得多
She seems to have got the better of you.

917
01:33:20,583 --> 01:33:23,245
暂时的 格兰蒂先生
For the moment, Mr. Grady.

918
01:33:23,985 --> 01:33:26,146
只是暂时的
Only for the moment.

919
01:33:28,056 --> 01:33:32,220
恐怕你不得不拿出最强硬的手段
I fear you will have to deal with this matter...

920
01:33:32,494 --> 01:33:36,156
来处理现在这种状况了 托兰斯先生
...in the harshest possible way, Mr. Torrance.

921
01:33:36,730 --> 01:33:38,288
恐怕
I fear...

922
01:33:38,565 --> 01:33:41,125
这也是你唯一能做的了
...that is the only thing to do.

923
01:33:44,604 --> 01:33:46,697
我可没期望过
There's nothing I look forward to...

924
01:33:46,906 --> 01:33:50,808
心平气和的解决这个问题 格兰蒂先生
...with greater pleasure, Mr. Grady.

925
01:33:52,210 --> 01:33:54,940
你确定 是么 托兰斯先生?
You give your word on that, do you, Mr. Torrance?

926
01:33:56,414 --> 01:33:58,439
我保证
I give you my word.

927
01:35:10,547 --> 01:35:13,107
Redrum

928
01:35:14,051 --> 01:35:16,610
Redrum

929
01:37:24,567 --> 01:37:26,125
丹尼 停下来
Danny, stop it!

930
01:38:22,919 --> 01:38:24,386
温蒂 我回来了
Wendy. I'm home.

931
01:39:01,721 --> 01:39:04,587
出来 管你在哪儿 快出来
Come out, come out, wherever you are.

932
01:39:30,146 --> 01:39:32,010
我出不来
I can't get out.

933
01:39:32,815 --> 01:39:33,941
快跑
Run!

934
01:39:34,783 --> 01:39:36,216
快跑呀 藏起来
Run and hide!

935
01:39:36,752 --> 01:39:37,878
快跑
Run!

936
01:39:38,086 --> 01:39:39,314
快
Quick!

937
01:39:41,022 --> 01:39:45,550
小猪猪 小猪猪 快让我进来 (儿歌)
Little pigs, little pigs, let me come in.

938
01:39:51,298 --> 01:39:54,699
不行 绝对不会开门的
Not by the hair on your chinny-chin-chin?

939
01:39:56,236 --> 01:39:58,295
那我就呼呼呼呼
Then I'll huff...

940
01:39:58,505 --> 01:40:00,404
吹呀吹
...and I'll puff...

941
01:40:00,606 --> 01:40:02,665
突然进到你的房子里来
...and I'll blow your house in!

942
01:40:17,588 --> 01:40:18,953
求你了
Please!

943
01:40:19,690 --> 01:40:21,453
别
Don't!

944
01:40:22,125 --> 01:40:23,649
别
Don't!

945
01:40:42,244 --> 01:40:43,472
住手
Stop it!

946
01:40:47,715 --> 01:40:49,273
小家伙在这里呀
Here's Johnny!

947
01:43:31,328 --> 01:43:32,556
哈罗?
Hello?

948
01:43:38,000 --> 01:43:39,763
有人在么?
Anybody here?

949
01:44:01,855 --> 01:44:03,412
哈罗?
Hello?

950
01:44:15,734 --> 01:44:17,565
有人在么?
Anybody here?

951
01:44:47,529 --> 01:44:49,463
有人在么?
Anybody here?

952
01:45:30,467 --> 01:45:32,162
丹尼小子
Danny-boy!

953
01:48:12,979 --> 01:48:14,913
我来了
I'm coming!

954
01:48:17,416 --> 01:48:19,350
我来了 丹尼
I'm coming, Dan!

955
01:49:20,139 --> 01:49:22,539
开派对 是吧?
Great party, isn't it?

956
01:49:40,191 --> 01:49:42,420
我来了
I'm coming!!

957
01:49:44,995 --> 01:49:47,293
你跑不掉了
You can't get away!

958
01:49:51,166 --> 01:49:53,566
我就在你背后
I'm right behind you!

959
01:53:18,585 --> 01:53:20,610
妈妈     丹尼 过来
Mommy!     Danny, come here!

960
01:53:21,821 --> 01:53:23,550
妈妈
Mommy.

961
01:53:31,897 --> 01:53:33,296
在哪儿?
Where...?

